---
title: Honey Mustard Glazed Pork with Mash, Sauteed Leeks and Cabbage
description: Our pan-fried pork loin is a comforting and hearty recipe great for cosy nights at home. With a creamy potato mash and sauteed leeks, this dish tastes indulgent but requires little fuss in the kitchen. Winner! Serve with a drizzle of apple and sage sauce and enjoy!
